^B@2^*Bhondo717: ^*N|cp||at|Not much to the play of this hand since diamonds break. 6C is a very good contract but Eddy made it difficult. Even if Elizabeth bids 3D, I will probably still bid 3N. In fact by bidding 3S, Elizabeth is showing a slightly stronger hand because she doesn't know I have that good a hand. The problem is I am not sure what slam we should be in. Although with my excellent clubs 6C probably has plays. But as I said Eddy's bid really stuck it to us. |
